## Error Handling

| Scenario | Behavior |
|----------|----------|
| NewsAPI returns 0 articles | Retry with broader query, abort if still 0 |
| Tagesschau RSS unreachable | Log warning, continue with NewsAPI only |
| LangChain timeout | Retry once before raising exception |
| Missing report sections | Regenerate report automatically |
| Resend delivery failure | Log error with status code |
| Missing env variables | Raise descriptive error on startup |

## API Costs & Limits

| API | Free Tier | Estimated Cost/Run |
|-----|-----------|-------------------|
| NewsAPI | 100 req/day | ~1 request |
| OpenAI GPT-4o-mini | Pay-per-use | ~$0.01 |
| OpenAI TTS | Pay-per-use | ~$0.05 |
| Resend | 100 emails/day | Free |
| Railway | $5 credit/month | Minimal |